Business > 
Industry Solutions









Your Business Is Unique. Our Business Is Keeping It That Way.
Every business is different. Every industry has its leaders. With tools and insights from a PlainsCapital banker, your business can play to its strengths, work more efficiently, and gain the extra edge that can make all the difference.





Nonprofit Organizations
PlainsCapital Bank offers banking solutions and investment management expertise to help you run a financially sound organization.









Professional Practices
Professionals need a strong bank partner that can support plans for expansion, provide resources for attracting and retaining top talent, and offer tools for improving operational efficiency.










Real Estate Investors
As a Texas-based bank, PlainsCapital Bank offers the unique advantage of understanding commercial real estate opportunities and trends in markets across the state.









Agricultural Businesses
PlainsCapital Bank provides loans to farmers and ranchers to finance equipment, land, or production expenses.










Wholesale Businesses
PlainsCapital Bank provides financing for industrial and commercial machinery, transportation, food and food products, medical supplies and devices as well as communications devices.









Financial Institutions
As your upstream correspondent bank, PlainsCapital Bank expands your bank’s access to funding, banking technology, and financial solutions for your customers.










Small Businesses
PlainsCapital Bank enjoys helping entrepreneurs take their businesses to the next level.









Manufacturing Businesses
PlainsCapital Bank works with manufacturing clients to provide flexible financial solutions that fit the cyclical nature of the manufacturing industry.










National Warehouse Lending
PlainsCapital’s experienced National Warehouse Lending staff provides warehouse facilities, efficient funding, and exceptional service to mortgage bankers throughout the country.




 



























